description:
This week on the podcast the guy’s are fresh off the road from the 1% workshop in Dallas. A workshop designed to help individuals live a life of abundance versus a life of lack. During the workshop Karl had his shining moment on stage and received a standing ovation for his presentation. This moment led to a conversation on how and when does someone make a turning point in their life. Many of you listen to this podcast weekly but you still haven’t made the turning point that will change your life. Grab your pen and pad and take notes so you can start taking the steps needed today.
